<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/32908877-margaret"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1404863110i/32908877._UY100_CR30,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
