<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/32908877-margaret">Margaret</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">His dilemma lay in that he had to take each instance separately. Ongoing vs closed. Hillary&apos;s emails were directly her. Trump was not the direct subje<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">His dilemma lay in that he had to take each instance separately. Ongoing vs closed. Hillary's emails were directly her. Trump was not the direct subject of the investigation at that time. He couldn't play tit for tat. Each situation had different lawful implications. The FBI is required to uphold the law as it is written, not as they would have it be. It totally sucks that the outcome was what it was, but he was damned if he did and damned if he didn't. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
